<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

    <head>
        <!-- Adding bootstrap CSS styles -->
        <link rel="stylesheet"
              href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
              integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T"
              crossorigin="anonymous">

        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport"
              content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

        <title>Sentence Pairs</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet"
              type="text/css"
              href="main.css" />
    </head>

    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <img class="margin-top-10percent width-10percent"
                         src="./media/horizontal_light.png" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <div class="col margin-top-5percent">
                    <h1 class="text-center text-primary-mid-green">Sentence Pair Evaluation</h1>
                    <div class="row justify-content-center">
                        <div class="col-sm-10 margin-top-5percent h4 text-primary-dark-grey">
                            <p>The evaluation is not timed and there is no time limit. However tests sets should be
                                completed in an unbroken single sitting.</p>
                            <p>Please start the test set when you will be able to give it your full attention, without
                                distraction, to completion.</p>
                            <p>If you have been asked to complete multiple test sets these don’t need to be done in a
                                continuous sitting.</p>
                            <p>If you are ready to complete an evaluation now enter your ID and select the test set you
                                have been asked to do. Then you’re ready to start.</p>
                            <p>Thank you again for your time. Your language and linguistic skills are crucial to the
                                success of this evaluation.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    {{!-- <h3 class="text-center text-primary-dark-grey margin-top-5percent">
                        Please enter your evaluator ID and select the sentence set you have been asked to evaluate
                    </h3> --}}
                    <form class="margin-top-5percent text-primary-dark-grey"
                          action="/beginEvaluation"
                          method="POST">
                        <div class="row justify-content-center form-group">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label for="evaluatorId">Enter your evaluator ID:</label>
                                <input class="form-control"
                                       name="evaluatorId"
                                       required>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row justify-content-center form-group">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <label for="setId">Pick the set you have been asked to
                                    evaluate:</label>
                                <select class="form-control"
                                        name="setId"
                                        required>
                                    <option></option>
                                    {{#each sentenceSets}}
                                    <option value="{{this.setId}}">{{this.name}}</option>
                                    {{/each}}
                                </select>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row justify-content-center form-group">
                            <div class="col-md-2">
                                <button type="submit"
                                        class="btn button-primary btn-block">Start
                                    Evaluation</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>

</html>